text.tspan: 4: Hide state 2.p1 in state 1.p1. This avoids motional sidebands from step 6
5: Hide state 2.n1 in state 1.n1. This avoids motional sidebands from step 6
7: Bring back state 2.p1 from hidden state 1.p1
8: Drive state 2.p1:2.p1, one second order motional sideband driven on
9: Bring back state 2.n1 from hidden state 1.n1
10: Drive state 2.n1:2.n1, one second order motional sideband driven on
18: Deshelve state 2.p1 to 2.p1, one second order motional sideband driven
20: Deshelve state 2.p2 to 2.p2, no others driven
